GlbList_ON_SearchUL [Name] - Global-list, sorted old->new, of all files
                             that Name has uploaded.

GlbList_ON_Unval [String]  - Global-list, sorted old->new, of all unvalidated
                             files.

GlbList_NO_All [Sig]       - Global-list, sorted new->old, of all files
                             in Sig.

GlbList_NO_New [Sig]       - Global-list, sorted new->old, of new files
                             in Sig.

GlbList_NO_Search [String] - Global-list, sorted new->old, of all files
                             matching string.

GlbList_NO_SearchUL [Name] - Global-list, sorted new->old, of all files
                             that Name has uploaded.

GlbList_NO_Unval [String]  - Global-list, sorted new->old, of all unvalidated
                             files.

GlbList_A_All [Sig]        - Global-list, sorted in alphabetic order, of all files
                             in Sig.

GlbList_A_New [Sig]        - Global-list, sorted in alphabetic order, of new files
                             in Sig.

GlbList_A_Search [String]  - Global-list, sorted in alphabetic order, of all files
